main event: One witness observed a round oval shaped white object with an exhaust trail for approximately 30 seconds.
interesting points: The object was less in diameter than the beam of a searchlight and just disappeared from sight., The object had an exhaust trail coming from it., The sighting was reported to the Town Marshall on 7-11-66., The witness was 20 years old at the time and saw the object while she was outdoors., No other witnesses confirmed seeing the object.
sighted object: a round oval shaped white object
witness description: A 20-year-old female who reported the sighting.
